overview: Private has changed its address, we’ve moved to the outskirts of the city to a quiet area where mansions and swimming pools are the least that you’ll find, and you know where that is… Temptation Avenue! What else could a street where Emily Belle, Sara Diamante, Kyle Green and Miriam Moore live be called. There’s no resisting temptation with these four babes around, and regardless of who it is, the neighbors, the gardeners, or just passersby, everyone is welcome for wild afternoons of sex where anal and DP are plenty!
title: Temptation Avenue
